LibraryGetFileLVVersion Method

Requires: Base Development System

Class: Application Methods (ActiveX)

Returns the version of LabVIEW in which the LabVIEW project library was created.

Syntax

object.LibraryGetFileLVVersion(libPath, [versNum])

Parameters

NameTypeDescription
libPathpathSpecifies the path to the library.
versNumLong*Returns the version number.

Return Value

String
